![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5c77ef5a-5b98-4e7a-b786-58aa1e49c8de/20240406_102134.jpg)

Giulia, a mainstay in Japan's prestigious STARDOM promotion, has sent shockwaves through the wrestling world with her highly anticipated arrival in WWE NXT.

NXT sources have confirmed to Fightful that Giulia will be reporting to the WWE Performance Center and NXT upon completion of her remaining dates, with an immediate main roster debut ruled out at this time.

The news comes after weeks of speculation and rumors surrounding the talented performer, whose name has been linked to a potential move to the global wrestling juggernaut.

Giulia's journey to WWE NXT marks the latest chapter in an already illustrious career. Hailing from Italy, she first made waves in the wrestling scene as part of the acclaimed STARDOM promotion, where she quickly rose through the ranks to become one of the company's top stars. Known for her ferocious in-ring style and commanding presence, Giulia has captivated audiences around the world with her electrifying performances and undeniable charisma.

The announcement of Giulia's arrival in WWE NXT comes amidst swirling rumors surrounding the future of STARDOM and its president, Rossy Ogawa. Speculation has been rife regarding Ogawa's plans to launch a new wrestling promotion, with reports suggesting that he has been scouting talent from various promotions, including STARDOM. This has led to speculation about potential talent acquisitions and the future direction of the Japanese wrestling landscape.

Giulia's decision to join WWE NXT adds further intrigue to the evolving landscape of professional wrestling, as fans eagerly anticipate her debut on the global stage. With her impressive track record and reputation as one of the brightest stars in the industry, Giulia has the potential to make a significant impact in NXT and beyond.

For Giulia, the move to WWE NXT represents an exciting opportunity to showcase her skills on a larger platform and take her career to new heights. As she prepares to step into the spotlight on NXT, fans can expect nothing short of greatness from this rising star.

As the wrestling world continues to buzz with excitement over Giulia's arrival in WWE NXT, one thing is certain: her presence will undoubtedly shake up the landscape of professional wrestling and leave an indelible mark on the industry for years to come.